🔗 Integration with the Builder's Log

The palace-graph.json is the source of truth for room locations. The Builder's Log references it:

```markdown
| File | Lvl | Visits | Palace Location |
|:---|:---|:---|:---|
| `Steal-No.md` | 🟦 L4 | 87 | East Library / Cracked Tablet |
